541,"uid":256393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"同咗個唔適合嘅人結婚先覺得係騙局"},{"pid":"38b7ef8aac9cc9237e91754abf24f6d245bcba63","tid":2025541,"uid":3112,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"每個人都係一件product，product最緊要有value<br />\n有啲係外觀靚，有啲就spec夠勁，有啲夠特別<br />\n但係點都好，有時買完會覺得唔岩用，又或者有defects<br />\n而且product總有一日會過時，亦有可能開始出現問題要拎去整，value就一直跌<br />\n<br />\n到時有啲人會選擇換個新款，有啲人就費時徙錢照用，有啲直頭dum左佢<br />\n你話拎去整？整乜鬼，分分鐘整仲貴過買新款<br />\n以前啲人就話會拎去整姐，宜家2020年喎<br />\n<br />\n最後諗諗：不如唔買算啦，反正我都係一時興起，慳返啲錢同時間做下其他野好過"},{"pid":"7a20b13571f3504574c70f3ea6e444d9ff16ea5c","tid":2025541,"uid":199926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"結婚咪同拍拖一樣<br />\n都係講價值講條件邊有咁多真愛"},{"pid":"d0d6f0b8ec4c94b29be18a90fbe7fabb564787e7","tid":2025541,"uid":303880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"457232d951ddfdcd2de7a369021928efc53cb63d","tid":2025541,"uid":251510,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"dcde0c57291e59ed287c32b41d5f0c8955805674","tid":2025541,"uid":240864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44924f10960cfe07bf0b3fff729078ab6043fb37","tid":2025541,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"More"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9374e1c4eb0349c6f83513eb9044233dd4092f2","tid":2025541,"uid":256362,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"88d49b60a1979cf77ccd3e0a48738ac92fea3bf3","tid":2025541,"uid":50744,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"結過<br />\n社會騙局黎<br />\n未結唔好結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"唔結好過結係真。<br />\n我知道最後無乜感情都真。<br />\n最後係求第次仆街撞親有人扶，病有人照顧。同埋合作生小朋友去maximize自己老咗有人睇住。<br />\n<br />\n除開一生恩愛嘅夫妻，對我嚟講婚姻係: <br />\n1. 組織家庭為感情生活同子女心靈牽引感上升<br />\n2. 有人睇住<br />\n3. 會有好多時候想一個人嘅時候，但單身唔可以隨時求有人陪，但結咗婚可以要求有人陪，同時亦可以有個人時間。<br />\n4. 正當解決生理需要<br />\n5. 有人了解同開解自己&mdash;心理需要<br />\n6. 獲取社會福利嘅單位<br />\n<br />\n有無其他？無了。<br />\n<br />\n其實我係對婚姻無信心，因為同上面巴打一樣，屋企都係離異，但我諗最後我都想結。最後離婚，我覺得都ok，當然盡量唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428022c5bb36f0a5738eb947e74d1284db49a0b4","tid":2025541,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a20b13571f3504574c70f3ea6e444d9ff16ea5c","tid":2025541,"uid":199926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"結婚咪同拍拖一樣<br />\n都係講價值講條件邊有咁多真愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"真？<br />\n咁點解要結婚"},{"pid":"78c44b88be2da132af204e3dd6ad59f4a38989f2","tid":2025541,"uid":55011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"唔相信人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52daff674c494d0c65562daca315a7cf4cfa14a6","tid":2025541,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44924f10960cfe07bf0b3fff729078ab6043fb37","tid":2025541,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"凡事及早解決就是。"},{"pid":"ecc5cc1e551a13644597abf519314435e64d46ef","tid":2025541,"uid":221647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"唔撚好結呀 屌老母"},{"pid":"a7cb85694bccfe8341cc7fec27f3984758d3b00c","tid":2025541,"uid":353929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"望住自己屋企人就冇左結婚既衝動<br />\n曾經好愛對方 但綁埋一齊過日子然後磨滅曬啲感情個種感覺好悲哀"},{"pid":"f318b3d548814ac0c599b810bb